      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that makes sense. It sounds pretty risky. Are there any specific words or phrases in that paragraph I should look out for that might make the liability even worse or more 'hidden' than it already seems? Like, is there any way they could use this to sneak in extra costs I wouldn't expect?",
